high_descs: Turn around and walk straight slightly then turn left and walk to the window and turn right to face the blue trash bin
Pick up the tissue box from the bottom of the trash bin
Turn around and walk straight then turn left at the kitchen table and face it
Place the tissue box on the kitchen table next to the box
Turn right walk straight slightly then turn left and walk forward then turn right at the sofa and walk to the TV
Pick up the tissue box from the TV stand
Turn right and walk straight slightly then turn right around the sofa and walk straight to the kitchen table and face it
Place the tissue box on the kitchen table next to the other tissue box

high_descs: Walk over to the small blue bin in the corner of the room behind you.
Pick up the box of tissues out of the blue bin.
Walk over to the far end of the large wooden table behind you.
Put the box of tissues on the large wooden table.
Walk over to the wooden table with the television on it across the room to your right.
Pick up the box of tissues off of the wooden table.
Walk back over to the end of the large wooden table behind you.
Put the box of tissues on the table next to the other box.
anns.task_desc: Move two boxes of tissues to a large wooden table.

high_descs: Turn around and walk left then face right to the trashcan.
Grab the tissue box out of the trashcan.
Turn around and walk along the table then turn and face left.
Place the tissue box on the table.
Turn right and walk then turn left and walk then go right again then right to face the TV stand.
Grab the tissue box from the TV stand.
Head right to get behind the couch then walk straight to the table then face right.
Place the second tissue box to the right of the first.
anns.task_desc: Place two tissue boxes on the table.
